My #HoneyDew this week is the one and only Joey Diaz! Joey has lived a life that very few, if any, have lived. I love talking with Joey because he's an open channel. I'll have him back again and we'll pick up right where we left off but when I tell you that the things Joey lived through and the things he did by age 9 are more than most adults have ever done in a lifetime, I'm not kidding. This episode is what the HoneyDew is all about. It's a must-listen and an instant classic! Subscribe, download & review!
